title: 10/08/21 DPS Hour 3 Brady Quinn

description:
Former Notre Dame QB/NFL QB and current Fox Sports Radio host of 2 Pro's & A Cup Of Joe, Brady Quinn talks to Dan about his days playing for Notre Dame. Brady also discusses the one TV show that he never understood but everyone loves.
